transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Ji sir good morning hello.
Customer: Hello. Good morning sir.
Executive: Gaurav baat kar raha hu sir.
Customer: Good morning.
Executive: Boliye sir. Hello. Kaise hai sir?
Customer: A sir. A abhi sir free hai aap?
Executive: Nahi thoda mai khana khata isliye
Customer: Tiffin khate hai.
Executive: Achha achha achha.
Executive: Aapko 10-15 minute me call kar lu?
Customer: Chalo.
Executive: Theek hai.
